data.description: Do not miss this adorable and efficient 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom 1978 bungalow with attached 1-car garage on a nicely fenced and private .15 acre lot. Conveniently located near the corner of N 9th St and Barr Ave in central Canon City for easy access to parks, schools, and shopping. Tile flooring in kitchen and bath, good sized kitchen with eat-in dining area, and extra deep garage with workbench. Double pane vinyl windows, forced air gas furnace, and central air conditioning provide year-round comfort. All kitchen appliances and washer and dryer are included! Come see the potential here for home ownership in this solid and affordable home, and make this one your own!
